---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import Header from "../components/Header.astro"
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro"
import ForumEventCard from "../components/ForumEventCard.astro"
import SectionColumned from "../components/SectionColumned.astro"

---

<Layout>
    <Header/>

    <main class="mx-auto max-w-[1024px]">
        <SectionColumned>
            <article class="prose pl-3">
                <h1 class="">About Us</h1>
                <div class="mt-0 text-xl">
                    <em> Supporting Professionals. Strengthening Recovery.</em>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-4">
                    The Professionals Platform convenes Class A Trustees of
                    Alcoholics Anonymous alongside cross-sector leaders who
                    support individuals with Alcohol Use Disorder (AUD). It
                    creates a space to inform and explore, strengthening and
                    advancing effective approaches to identification and
                    support.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4">
                    Many of us are professionals ourselves or were guided to
                    recovery through professional referral.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4">
                    We recognize the critical role of professionals across
                    systems and settings, including:
                </p>
                <ul class="mr-16 ">
                    <li class="mt-3">
                        <strong>Workplace & Organizational Leaders</strong> — human
                        resources professionals, Employee Assistance Program (EAP)
                        providers, and C-suite leaders, directors, and managers
                    </li>
                    <li class="mt-3">
                        <strong>Healthcare & Behavioral Health</strong> — healthcare
                        providers, behavioral health practitioners, and social workers
                    </li>
                    <li class="mt-3">
                        <strong>Public Safety & First Response</strong> — fire, police,
                        and other frontline professionals
                    </li>
                    <li class="mt-3">
                        <strong>Legal & Justice Systems</strong> — legal, judicial,
                        corrections, probation, and reentry professionals
                    </li>
                    <li class="mt-3">
                        <strong>Education & Community Institutions</strong> — university
                        and higher education administrators, faculty, student support
                        services, and nonprofit and community-based organization leaders
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-4">
                    This platform provides a forum to learn, listen, and share
                    practical approaches that support professionals on the front
                    lines of recovery.
                </p>
            </article>

            <div class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-100 to-gray-050 px-4 pt-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Contact Us:</h3>
                <p><a href="mailto:info@professionalsplatform.org" class="link">info@professionalsplatform.org</a></p>

                <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold">A.A. Links</h3>
                <p>
                    <a
                        href="https://www.aa.org/Cooperation-with-the-Professional-Community" class="link"
                        target="_blank"
                        >Cooperation with the Professional Community (CPC)
                    </a>
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4">
                    <a
                        href="https://www.aa.org/public-information-committees"
                         class="link"
                        target="_blank">Public Information Committees</a
                    >
                </p>
            </div>
        </SectionColumned>
    </main>
    <Footer/>

    <style>
        .hero {
            background:
                linear-gradient(
                    92deg,
                    #b9dfe9 30%,
                    rgba(153, 211, 224, 0.75) 60%,
                    rgba(8, 81, 113, 0.3) 94.45%
                ),
                url("/images/mono-chairs-1600.jpg") lightgray 50% / cover
                    no-repeat;
        }
    </style>
</Layout>
